window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Death isn't always permanent, and second chances don't come free. </p> <p>The system gives Dare no answers, only orders. The other eels are equally as unforthcoming, and Dare must resort to dangerous methods to uncover hidden information, taking chances that risk death if the system in their head disapproves. </p> <p>By poking at the holes in the Second Chance (SC) system, Dare discovers just how blurry its morality truly is. For anyone to escape, itâ€™ll take working together. </p> <p>But not everyone wants to be freed, and SC has worked too hard, too long, to give any of them up.</p>"; 
